{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The other one were criminals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had a red and a yellow triangle on top of each other with a number.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And say we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were others who had red ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were also political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there were purple ones and black ones and, you know, all sorts of homosexuals, and those who were there for religious reasons, outcasts, I'm not sure, priests-- a number of triangles.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I didn't make a study of it then, and so I cannot be asked details now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, these were probably the rooms of the block elders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went through a small door into that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were undressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we already had filled up nicely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my father said, put out your tummy to look even better than you are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my father also had to wait, and he was behind me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I stepped through the door, and I saw the SS doctor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And next to him, the block eldest as he was called, block eldester.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the SS man's thumb went accordingly to the right or to the left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And to the right were the people were the healthy-looking people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And to the left were those who one could see they were, well, he selected for the gas chambers to be cured.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in front of me was a fellow who looked much better than the one in the front of him who passed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But for some reason, the, the SS man turned, and his thumb went to the left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the helpers who who stood by pushed him into the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "For them there's-- they couldn't care anymore-- into the other little part of the room with the condemned.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
